main event: Multiple UFO sightings were reported on September 17th, 1955, in Bellingham, Washington.
interesting points: The sightings described round, white to red objects with no sound or trail, following a level course.
Descriptions included objects being purple, fuzzy, and still under observation at a 45 degree, 30 degree angle.
The witness, a 35-year-old male, made note that no photographs were submitted with the report.
An analysis suggested that the UFO sightings may have been the result of jets being launched in the area.
Though there were no conclusive photographs, there were multiple witnesses and detailed observations of the unidentified objects.
sighted object: round, white to red UFOs following a level course
photographs: no photographs submitted with the report
